remarks.format: ## Remarks 既不是 InstanceOwnerException 也不是 InstancePersistenceCommandException 的 InstancePersistenceException 會套用至持續性提供者本身，也可以表示提供者無法復原的失敗狀況。An InstancePersistenceException that is not an InstanceOwnerException nor an InstancePersistenceCommandException applies to the persistence provider itself and may indicate an unrecoverable failure condition of the provider.
